data.title: What is the climate like in Russian Siberia?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): Siberia is a HUGE place.

And thus, there is not just one climate in Siberia.

As a rule of thumb, you can go by the following:

 * Winters are something in between cold, very cold, and super cold to the tune of Yakutsk - Wikipedia being, in wintertime, THE coldest big city on Ea...
